        DEDICATED TO THE MEN OF THE SOUTH WHO SUFFERED EXILE. IMPRISONMENT AND
        DEATH FOR THE DARING SERVICE THEY RENDERED OUR COUNTRY AS CITIZENS OF
        THE INVISIBLE EMPIRE
      </p>
